# Financial Risk Credit On Balance Sheet Expected Losses Purchased Receivables Amount

## identifier
de7956

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of expected losses from on-balance sheet credit exposures arising from purchased receivables.

This item is reported for capital adequacy purposes and is to be determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.OnBalanceSheetExpectedLossesPurchasedReceivables.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
